public class ServletContextWrapper

getResourcePaths

public Set getResourcePaths(String thePath)
Added to support the changes of the Jakarta Servlet API 2.3 of the 17/03/2001 (in anticipation of the upcoming draft of Servlet 2.3). Kept the method without parameters for servlet engines that do not have upgraded yet to the new signature.
